reviewText:
This is a great VHS with Bugs and Elmer's early battles.

1. Wabbit Twouble (Clampett, 1941)
2. The Big Snooze (Clampett, 1946)
3. Fresh Hare (Freleng, 1942)
4. The Unruly Hare (Tashlin, 1945)
5. Slick Hare (Freleng, 1947)
6. Hare Remover (Tashlin, 1946)
7. Stage Door Cartoon (Freleng, 1944)
